    <h1>
     <a href="http://about.blogs.rice.edu/2015/06/26/comments-off/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Comments Off!">
      Comments Off!
     </a>
    </h1>
    <div class="post-inner">
     <a href="http://about.blogs.rice.edu/2015/06/26/comments-off/">
     </a>
     <p>
      So, you’ve been creating posts and pages like crazy and suddenly realize there are comment boxes on every page.  If you are using the CampusPress suite for your club or department web page,
      <a href="http://help.edublogs.org/enable-and-disable-comments-on-future-posts-and-pages/">
       you can turn off comments for all future pages and posts
      </a>
      , but you still have to fix every existing page.  Here’s how.
      <br/>
      <a href="http://about.blogs.rice.edu/files/2015/06/CommentsOff-QuickEdit-1byrldn.png">
       <img alt="CommentsOff-QuickEdit" class="alignleft wp-image-330 size-full" height="239" sizes="(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px" src="http://about.blogs.rice.edu/files/2015/06/CommentsOff-QuickEdit-1byrldn.png" srcset="http://about.blogs.rice.edu/files/2015/06/CommentsOff-QuickEdit-1byrldn.png 360w, http://about.blogs.rice.edu/files/2015/06/CommentsOff-QuickEdit-1byrldn-300x199.png 300w, http://about.blogs.rice.edu/files/2015/06/CommentsOff-QuickEdit-1byrldn-346x230.png 346w" style="padding: 15px;" width="360"/>
      </a>
     </p>
     <p>
      From the Dashboard menu, select “All Pages” or “All Posts” to get the full list.
     </p>
     <ol>
      <li>
       Use the Quick Edit selection for each post or page.
      </li>
      <li>
       Uncheck the Allow Comments box, then click Update.
      </li>
     </ol>
     <p>
      <a href="http://about.blogs.rice.edu/files/2015/06/CommentsOff-QuickEdit-UPDATE-qcwduj.png">
       <img alt="CommentsOff-QuickEdit-UPDATE" border="1" class="alignleft wp-image-331 size-full" height="161" sizes="(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px" src="http://about.blogs.rice.edu/files/2015/06/CommentsOff-QuickEdit-UPDATE-qcwduj.png" srcset="http://about.blogs.rice.edu/files/2015/06/CommentsOff-QuickEdit-UPDATE-qcwduj.png 576w, http://about.blogs.rice.edu/files/2015/06/CommentsOff-QuickEdit-UPDATE-qcwduj-300x84.png 300w, http://about.blogs.rice.edu/files/2015/06/CommentsOff-QuickEdit-UPDATE-qcwduj-540x151.png 540w" style="padding: 15px;" width="576"/>
      </a>
     </p>
     <div addthis:title="Comments Off! " addthis:url="http://about.blogs.rice.edu/2015/06/26/comments-off/" class="addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style addthis_32x32_style">
