   <article class="post-306 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-start category-migration" id="post-306">
    <a href="http://about.blogs.rice.edu/2015/06/01/migration-complete/">
     <div class="date-tab">
      <span class="month">
       June
      </span>
      <span class="day">
       1
      </span>
     </div>
     <!-- .date-tab -->
    </a>
    <h1>
     <a href="http://about.blogs.rice.edu/2015/06/01/migration-complete/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Migration Complete!">
      Migration Complete!
     </a>
    </h1>
    <div class="post-inner">
     <a href="http://about.blogs.rice.edu/2015/06/01/migration-complete/">
     </a>
     <p>
      <a href="http://about.blogs.rice.edu/files/2015/05/Butterflies-44552314-small.jpg">
       <img alt="Rainbow Butterflies" border="1" class="alignleft wp-image-300 size-medium" height="300" sizes="(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px" src="http://about.blogs.rice.edu/files/2015/05/Butterflies-44552314-small-200x300.jpg" srcset="http://about.blogs.rice.edu/files/2015/05/Butterflies-44552314-small-200x300.jpg 200w, http://about.blogs.rice.edu/files/2015/05/Butterflies-44552314-small.jpg 216w" style="PADDING-LEFT: 5px; PADDING-RIGHT: 5px;" width="200"/>
      </a>
      <br/>
      Welcome to your new home!  Your content in blogs.rice.edu was migrated for you over the weekend.  Your new home in the cloud is being hosted on CampusPress by EduBlogs, a robust platform that includes many popular themes, plug-ins, widgets and other features.  Check out about.blogs.rice.edu for more details.
     </p>
     <p>
      To get started, just
      <a href="http://blogs.rice.edu/wp-login.php">
       login to blogs.rice.edu
      </a>
      and update your site, change the theme, add a plug-in, or simply enjoy the new features like adding content from your mobile device.
     </p>
     <p>
      New to blogging?
      <a href="http://blogs.rice.edu/wp-login.php">
       Login to blogs.rice.edu
      </a>
      , then create your first web site or blog by clicking Dashboard &gt; Create a New Site.
     </p>
     <p>
      Questions?  Please contact the Help Desk:
      <a href="mailto:helpdesk@rice.edu">
       helpdesk@rice.edu
      </a>
      or 713.348.4357 and include the link to your site in the request.
     </p>
     <div addthis:title="Migration Complete! " addthis:url="http://about.blogs.rice.edu/2015/06/01/migration-complete/" class="addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style addthis_32x32_style">
