    <h1>
     <a href="http://about.blogs.rice.edu/2015/03/18/get-started/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Getting Started">
      Getting Started
     </a>
    </h1>
    <div class="post-inner">
     <a href="http://about.blogs.rice.edu/2015/03/18/get-started/">
     </a>
     <p>
      Start blogging today with a new blog, or continue updating your previous blog. Use your Rice NetID to
      <a href="http://blogs.rice.edu">
       login: https://blogs.rice.edu
      </a>
      .
     </p>
     <p>
      <iframe frameborder="0" height="264" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/NjwUHXoi8lM" width="469">
      </iframe>
     </p>
